    subgraph ap["AP-biased (availability first)"]
        R[Mailbox read replicas<br/>cached threads]
        S[Search index<br/>eventual]
        F[Spam scores<br/>stale OK / policy fallback]
    end
    CLIENT[Client / MTA] --> Q
    Q --> M
    M --> R
    M --> S
    M --> F
